'''心理成熟'''是指[[心理|心理]]指随着时间的推移向着圆满生长，有能力以恰当的方式对[[社会环境|社会环境]]做出适当反应。反应通常而言是靠學習而得到的，而非先天[[本能|本能]]。成熟也意味着根据情况和社会文化，知道做出某行为的正确时间和场所。<ref name="Wechsler1950">{{cite journal|last=Wechsler|first=David|title=Intellectual Development and Psychological Maturity|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_child-development_1950-03_21_1/page/45|journal=Child Development|date=1 March 1950|volume=21|issue=1|pages=45|doi=10.2307/1126418|jstor=1126418}}</ref>成熟强调对生活目的、方向有清楚的认识，从而感到生活是有意义的。<ref>{{cite web | last = Adler | first = Nancy | authorlink =  | coauthors =  | title = Purpose in Life | work = Psychosocial workgroup | publisher = MacArthur | date = November 1997 | url = http://www.macses.ucsf.edu/research/psychosocial/purpose.php | accessdate = 2011-11-03 | archive-date = 2019-03-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190322053400/https://www.macses.ucsf.edu/research/psychosocial/purpose.php | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

